    <h2 class="mt-5">Delete cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">Most cookies have an expiration date. This means that they expire automatically after a certain period and no longer record data from your site visit. You can also choose to manually delete the cookies before the expiry date has expired. For more information about this, please consult your browser manual.</p>

